wikiText:
"Television Rules The Nation / Crescendolls" is the third track of thirteen on Daft Punk's, 'Alive 2007' album.
 
 The album was recorded live Paris, France at Bercy.
 
 The track is a mash-up of their tracks, "Television Rules The Nation", "Crescendolls" and a vocal from "Around The World."
